Date Range (start date and end date).
Single Date for daily summaries.
Category or source filters (e.g., show only "Salary" income or "Food" expenses).
Implement sorting options:
Ascending/descending by amount or date.
A toggle between "Daily", "Weekly", and "Monthly" views.
UI Elements: Dropdowns, date pickers, and buttons.

